<br>
Cait, no discussions of testing occurred in any of the original policy discussion threads or the threads on moderating or administrating; so it wasn't part of policy from the beginning that mods be tested.  I saw QT make a suggestion and comment in this thread regarding testing.  In my first post in the thread, I made a suggestion regarding the process, if the membership decided testing was needed.  So far most of the responses here suggest it might not be needed.<br>
<br>
Further, moderating here is not my job.  I volunteered to do it, as did most of the rest of the mods.  Practical experience in moderating is best learned by moderating; just as practical experience in adminstrating is best learned by administrating.  <br>
<br>
This decision wasn't harmless; it has cost us a moderator.  Moreover, it seems clear that the administrators involved have violated the stated policies created by consensus and now claim that violation was harmless.  They have also added a clause allowing them to change the policy at will which directly contradicts earlier statements in the policy.<br>
<br>
Your last statement about a &quot;wide open door to chaos&quot; is a slippery slope fallacy.  <br>
<br>
Consubstantial <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.showMessageRange?topicID=39.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.showMessageRange?topicID=39.topic&start=41&stop=51>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.showPrevMessage?topicID=39.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=39.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.emailToFriend?topicID=39.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.threadControl?topicID=39.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=39.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm16.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=39.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td al